We get warm, nostalgic fuzzies from 8mm Vintage Cameras grainy, flickery film filters and lens effects, conjuring up memories of vacation travelogues screened in wood-paneled basements. Its not just about old-school kicks, thoughthis powerful suite of tools can give any video an authentic period look.
